The paper discusses the use of Artificial Intelligence (AI) algorithms for automated scoring of Human epidermal growth factor receptor 2 (Her2) in breast cancer tissues. This involves the analysis of digitized whole slide images (WSI) of breast cancer tissues stained with both Haematoxylin & Eosin (H&E) and IHC for Her2. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Other likely sub-categories include cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.DL (Deep Learning), as these sub-categories are also relevant to the use of AI algorithms for automated image analysis and scoring.
